{%- doc -%}
  Versioned URLs for the shared RX modules. Inter-module imports can't use
  plain relative paths: unversioned asset URLs are CDN-cached for a year, so a
  deploy would leave returning visitors importing stale modules. RX entry
  modules read this map and dynamically import the versioned URL instead
  (falling back to the relative path when the map is absent, e.g. under tests).

  Safe to render more than once per page — consumers read the first occurrence.
{%- enddoc -%}

<script type="application/json" data-rx-imports>
  {
    "rx-core.js": {{ 'rx-core.js' | asset_url | json }},
    "rx-api.js": {{ 'rx-api.js' | asset_url | json }}
  }
</script>
